# ============================================================
# F3 — Rules A-E: substrate-aware routing (M3.52 + M3.53 + M3.54)
# ============================================================
#
# Five router rules now compose at every dispatch boundary:
#   A. action-safety (warn → bump rung up)
#   B. ceiling-cap < threshold → force voter
#   C. daftar disagreement > threshold → bump rung up
#   D. quota near exhaustion → quota-fallback
#   E. value-of-inquiry < threshold → decline-and-propose-alternative

